metadata.name: SPLOSIONS #1/69
metadata.description: SPLOSIONS is a splash of color in the form of 69 globulous sploinks of ai-generated Art on the Ethereum Splockchain. Curated from hundreds of spills, splotches, and splatters, SPLOSIONS splodes in splendid sprays of spectrums beyond imagination. No roadmap, no utility, no Discord, just Art for Art's sake. Created and Curated by madchops.eth.
